quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  104,7,"èyí tí ó máa jó (ẹ̀dá) wọ inú ọkàn lọ."
  104,8,"Dájúdájú wọ́n máa ti (àwọn ìlẹ̀kùn) Iná pa mọ́ wọn lórí pátápátá."
  104,9,"(Wọ́n máa wà) láààrin àwọn òpó kìrìbìtì gíga (nínú Iná)."
  105,4,"Wọ́n ń jù wọ́n ní òkúta amọ̀ (tó ti gbaná sára)."
  105,5,"Ó sì sọ wọ́n di bíi pòpórò gbígbẹ tí ẹranko jẹ lájẹdàsílẹ̀."
  106,1,"(Ìkẹ́ ni láti ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu) fún ìdílé Ƙuraeṣ láti wà papọ̀ nínú ààbò."
  106,2,"(Ìkẹ́ ni sẹ́ láti ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu) fún wọn láti wà papọ̀ nínú ààbò lórí ìrìn-àjò ní ìgbà òtútù àti ní ìgbà ooru."
  106,3,"Nítorí náà, kí wọ́n jọ́sìn fún Olúwa Ilé (Ka‘bah) yìí."